                  <div class="text-wrapper">
                      <header>
              
  <h2 class="field field-type-text field-label-hidden tile-field-title">
    How we protect your personal information  </h2>
            </header>
                    
  <div class="field field-type-text-long field-label-hidden tile-field-text copy"><p></p><div class="media media-element-container media-default media-float-right media-wysiwyg-align-right"><img height="3013" width="3573" style="height: 126px; width: 150px; float: right;" class="media-element file-default default-embedded" data-delta="1" src="https://www.edfenergy.com/sites/default/files/cyber-essentials-badge-high-res.png" alt="" /></div>EDF Energy takes the protection of our customer’s information very seriously.<p>For security reasons, as with all organisations, it wouldn’t be appropriate for us to disclose specific details as to how we protect information. We’ve taken a ‘defence in depth’ approach to Information Security, especially regarding our online services.</p><p>Our systems are kept up-to-date and we test our online services to make sure they’re secure and that unauthorised access is prevented.</p></div>
      </div>
